mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: With every win in The Arena, the rewards are getting better up to 12 wins
mxTextCell.prevLabel: With every win in The Arena, the rewards are getting better up to 12 wins

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: When the player wins a game, he is matched against an opponent with the same number of wins therefore the chance of winning decreases
mxTextCell.prevLabel: When the player wins a game, he is matched against an opponent with the same number of wins therefore the chance of winning decreases

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: The player can win a maximum of 12 games and lose a maximum of 3 games before a run is over and the player receives his rewards based on the number of wins
mxTextCell.prevLabel: The player can win a maximum of 12 games and lose a maximum of 3 games before a run is over and the player receives his rewards based on the number of wins

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: Even if a player didn't win a single game, he can still earn rewards
mxTextCell.prevLabel: Even if a player didn't win a single game, he can still earn rewards

mxTextCell.title: Text
mxTextCell.label: Rewards are splitting to 2 catagories :- a standard reward- one or two random rewards from pools
mxTextCell.prevLabel: Rewards are splitting to 2 catagories :- a standard reward- one or two random rewards from pools
